<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>fú shì zhǔ yé sū bù néng lěng dàn 迦南538</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 fú shì zhǔ yé sū bù néng lěng dàn, bèi qǐ shí zì jià bù néng zì lián,
 bù jiàn tiān fù miàn bù néng xiē xī zhēn xī měi tiān fèng xiàn měi tiān,
 rén shēng zài shì rú guò lù kè, shì jiè xū huàn rú yún rú yān,
 shí zhōng kuài zǒu xiàng bèi tí de zhōng diǎn, wǒ men dōu yào nǔ lì wǎng qián gǎn.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>538</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>